Output tail_vs_peacock.gif

Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 18
Set FontFamily "JetBrainsMono Nerd Font Mono"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 400
Set Padding 1


Type "tail dummy.log"

Sleep 1s

Enter

Sleep 3s

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "peacock dummy.log"

Sleep 1s

Enter

Screenshot peacock_screenshot.png

Sleep 3s
